data.description: Your Private Mountain Oasis Awaits in the heart of California's Gold Country. Escape to this secluded 10-acres, where nature's artistry meets modern comfort. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1772 sq ft home offers stunning panoramic Sierra Nevada Mountain views and a tranquil seasonal creek.  Rustic Elegance: Elevate your lifestyle with newer upgrades including a composition roof, an oversized HVAC unit, and owned solar panels (2018) for sustainable living. Cozy up by the wood stove on winter evenings with views of the snow-capped Sierras.  Pure Mountain Water: A reliable onsite well, equipped with a newer pump (2020), ensures your water needs are met. Enjoy the luxury of a water softener system and ample water with two large storage tanks.  Your Personal Haven: Explore endless possibilities with a spacious workshop complete with power and water. Protect your RV with a convenient storage cover. Delight in an orchard graced by mature fruit trees, perfect for harvesting your own fresh produce. Embrace Mountain Living: Indulge in the simplicity of county living - serenity, sustainability, and natural beauty. This home epitomizes the art of tranquil living in the heart of the Sierra Nevada Mountains. Claim your oasis today.
